---
// src/pages/reviews/airtag-2-review.astro
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="AirTag 2 Review 2026 - Longer Range & Louder Sound">
  <article class="review">
    <header class="review-header">
      <span class="category">Accessories</span>
      <h1>AirTag 2 Review: Better Than Ever</h1>
      <div class="meta">
        <span>By ReviewCloud Team</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>March 6, 2026</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="rating">
      <span class="score">4.5</span>
      <span class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</span>
    </div>

    <div class="price-banner">
      <span class="price">$29 (Single)</span>
      <span class="release">Available Now</span>
    </div>

    <div class="toc">
      <h2>Table of Contents</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#overview">Overview</a></li>
        <li><a href="#features">New Features</a></li>
        <li><a href="#verdict">Verdict</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <section id="overview">
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>Apple's all-new <strong>AirTag 2</strong> is here with significant improvements over the original. Launched in January 2026, it addresses user feedback with longer range and a louder speaker.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="features">
      <h2>What's New</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Longer Range</strong>: Improved U1 chip offers better tracking distance</li>
        <li><strong>Louder Speaker</strong>: Easier to find when lost</li>
        <li><strong>Same Great Features</strong>: Precision Finding, Lost Mode, IP67 water resistance</li>
      </ul>
      <p>The original AirTag is still available at discounted prices, with 4-packs now available for just $64 on Amazon.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="verdict">
      <h2>Verdict</h2>
      <p>AirTag 2 is a solid upgrade for anyone who needs help keeping track of their belongings. It's especially useful for:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Keys and wallets</li>
        <li>Luggage during travel</li>
        <li>Backpacks and bags</li>
        <li>Bicycles and other valuables</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="buy-links">
        <h3>Where to Buy</h3>
        <a href="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=AirTag+2&tag=reviewcloud-20" class="buy-btn" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">
          Buy on Amazon
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .review { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem; background: white; }
  .review-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .category { background: #667eea; color: white; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.875rem; }
  .review-header h1 { font-size: 2rem; margin: 1rem 0; }
  .meta { color: #666; display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; justify-content: center; }
  .rating { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; padding: 1.5rem; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 12px; }
  .score { font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 700; color: #667eea; }
  .stars { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-left: 1rem; }
  .price-banner { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; background: #e8f5e9; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .price { font-weight: 700; color: #2e7d32; font-size: 1.25rem; }
  .release { color: #666; }
  .toc { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .toc h2 { font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .toc ul { list-style: none; }
  .toc li { padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
  .toc a { color: #667eea; text-decoration: none; }
  section { margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  section h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  section p { color: #555; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  ul { margin: 1rem 0; padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { margin: 0.5rem 0; color: #555; }
  .buy-links { text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem; padding: 2rem; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 12px; }
  .buy-btn { display: inline-block; padding: 1rem 3rem; background: #ff9900; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; }
  .buy-btn:hover { background: #e68a00; }
</style>
